line_1: And all the town rings of his swearing and roaring,
line_2: 'They say he's no Christian, loves drinking and whoring,

line_1: 'What a pother is here about wenching and roaring!
line_2: Why David loved catches and Solomon whoring.

line_1: Then what a Plague make thee a roaring,
line_2: And scribling on my Fubses whoring;
